 futures.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 07. Nov 2022) 0aRashāyidah (Arab people). 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aAnthropology of Uncertainty, Sudan, Rashaida, Uncertainty, Development, Precarity.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBerghahn Books Complete eBook-Package 2016z978311099822140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781785330162?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781785330162423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781785330162/original  a978-3-11-099822-1  Berghahn Books Complete eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK